#$_GET --> Data is appended to the url
           NOT Secure
           char limit
           bookmark is possible
           it can be cached
           better for a search page

#$_POST --> Data is packaged inside the body of the html page
            It is Secure
            no data limit
            cannot bookmark
            requests are not cached
            better for form 

 #Logical Operators:
          --> &&
          --> ||
          --> !

//Cookie --> Information about a user stored in a user's web-browser targeted advertisements, browsing preferences, & other sensitive data